## ADMIN USER - Manage Users

[X] - Should have a users list to be manage , each should be dynamic.
[X] - Should be possible to filter the users list by email or username.
[X] - Can change the roles of the user from unsigned to regular in the users list.
[X] - Can block an user from bad behavior in the users list.

## ADMIN USER - Manage Categories

[X] - Should have a categories list to be manage , each should be dynamic.
[x] - Can add a new category in the categories list for the app.
[x] - Can delete a category in the categories list of the app.

## ADMIN USER - Manage Notifications

[] - Should have a list of options of each type of notifications to be configured.
[] - Can choose the type of notification to be sent to the users
(daily content - added photo to an album of followed user,
comment photos - comments on liked photos
favorite album - new photo added to a favorite album
, viewed profile - content of viewed profile
).
[] - daily content - added photo to an album of followed user
[] - comment photos - comments on liked photos
[] - favorite album - new photo added to a favorite album
[] - viewed profile - content of viewed profile

## ALL USERS - Authentication

[X] - Should have a login page to be authenticated.
[X] - Should have a register page to be authenticated.
[X] - Can Sign In with email and password.
[X] - Can Sign Up with username, email and password.
[X] - Can Sign Out.
[X] - Should be possibile to navigate to register window from login window.
[X] - Should be possible to navigate to login window from register window.
[X] - Restrict access to the app if the user is not authenticated.
[X] - If the logged user is blocked should display an Account Suspension Notice.
[] - Blocked User should have the possibility to contact the admin to try unblock the account.
[X] - Restrict acess to some features, each only admin can access - Manage Users, Manage Categories, Manage Notifications.
[] - Unsigned User can access all the features but have limited access in the catalog of content, each means, can only view the feature photos (top 5 - most liked photos)

## ALL USERS - Profile

[X] - An user should have an avatar.
[X] - Should have the possibility of updating his avatar.
[] - An user should have the possibility to chance his password access.
[X] - An user should be possible to create an album of photos.
[X] - Display the albuns availabe of the user.
[X] - Change the name of an album.
[X] - Number of followers.
[X] - Delete content (only is possible to delete content created by the user). - delete photo from an album
[X] - Display favorite albuns.
[X] - For the admin profile should display the list of contacts of banned users.

## ALL USERS - Manage Content

[] - Add content with short description (max 150chars), date of published, a category associated and an image(Photo). - Add Photo to an album
[] - Should display "gallery" of random photos in the catalog.
[] - Should be possible to see the detail of a clicked photo from the "gallery" :

- () the photo (image)
- () number views
- () number likes
- () number comments
- () author of the photo
- () button (like)
- () button ( add comment )
- () button (see setail of the photo)
  [] - Display the detail of the photo:
- () the photo (image)
- () number views
- () number likes
- () description
- () number comments
- () author of the photo
- () button (like)
- () button ( add comment )
- () see threat of comments

## ALL USERS - Filter Content

[] - Filter By user the catalog of content. (search)
[] - Filter By category the catalog of content. (select)

## ALL USERS - Interaction with the content

[] - Can add comment to a photo of an other user album.
[] - Can add a like to a photo of an other user album.
[] - Each photo should have a thread of comments.
[] - Should sent a notification if a user interact (reply of a comment)
[] - The users can reply to previous comments.
